      "id": "sybil_17_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it's a total dream. This car is in truly incredible shape\u2014it looks and drives just like it did the day it rolled off the lot! I've kept it garage-tucked and pampered, so it's spotless inside and out. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the sticker shock, this is the one. I'm super easy to work with and happy to answer any questions you have. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
