    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Available is an exceptional E46 M3, showcasing the high-revving S54B32 power plant with its signature individual throttle bodies and high-velocity induction. This specimen features a meticulously documented service history, including a proactive VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement to ensure long-term mechanical integrity. The chassis is bolstered by comprehensive subframe reinforcement, while the 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox delivers precise, mechanical shifts through a refreshed linkage. Every component, from the M-variable differential lock to the suspension bushings, operates at factory tolerances. This is a collector-grade chassis with flawless paint depth and an immaculate engine bay, representing the pinnacle of naturally aspirated BMW engineering.",
